snippet.title: EXOME Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist and Follow: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1761900/EXOME/
EXOME is a co-op survival shooter with a focus on exploration, weapon progression and horde AI. Discover what grim mysteries are hidden in this deep forest. Explore and fight for survival, alone or with your friends.
